{"type":"message","id":"e3ddbf8e","parentId":"4fb57c2d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:20:39.842Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i691yra5jjku_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4237\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2370\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[master 70a369b] pulse: 2026-03-24 152016\n 6 files changed, 296 insertions(+), 86 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 152016.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 152016.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 151918.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 152016 - The previous binary threshold experiment revealed that CFI � 0.7 AND freq < 60 is too aggressive (loses 92.9% recall). The key insight is that \"Phase 1\" (freq=136, CFI=0.96) is true research trajectory being crushed by the freq < 60 filter. The hybrid scoring formula needs testing.\r\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"marine-meadow","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4237\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2370\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[master 70a369b] pulse: 2026-03-24 152016\n 6 files changed, 296 insertions(+), 86 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 152016.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 152016.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 151918.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 152016 - The previous binary threshold experiment revealed that CFI � 0.7 AND freq < 60 is too aggressive (loses 92.9% recall). The key insight is that \"Phase 1\" (freq=136, CFI=0.96) is true research trajectory being crushed by the freq < 60 filter. The hybrid scoring formula needs testing.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":fal