{"type":"message","id":"c1265b8b","parentId":"ada590cb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:20:48.749Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5vrfg0921k7w_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"the\n---\n[NEW_FILE]\n---\n# CFI×Freq Hybrid Scoring Experiment (Strategy C)\n# Test: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120) vs binary thresholds\n# Hypothesis: Hybrid scoring distinguishes \"constant format\" from \"research trajectory\"\n\n$EXPERIMENT_DIR = \"$PSScriptRoot\"\n$STATE_DIR = \"$EXPERIMENT_DIR/../state\"\n$PULSES_DIR = \"$STATE_DIR/pulses\"\n$OUTPUT_FILE = \"$EXPERIMENT_DIR/CFI_FREQ_HYBRID_RESULTS.md\"\n\n# Load all pulses\n$pulseFiles = Get-ChildItem -Path $PULSES_DIR -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | Sort-Object Name\nWrite-Host \"Loaded $($pulseFiles.Count) pulses\"\n\nif ($pulseFiles.Count -eq 0) {\n    Write-Host \"ERROR: No pulses found\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# Build token corpus with CFI and frequency\n$tokenData = @{}\n$tokenDocs = @{}  # token -> count of docs it appears in\n\nforeach ($pf in $pulseFiles) {\n    $content = Get-Content $pf.FullName -Raw\n    $docTokens = @{}\n    \n    # Tokenize (simple whitespace split + trim punctuation)\n    $tokens = $content -split '\\s+' | ForEach-Object { $_.Trim() -replace '^[^\\w]+|[^\\w]+$', '' } | Where-Object { $_.Length -gt 2 }\n    \n    foreach ($t in $tokens) {\n        if (-not $tokenData.ContainsKey($t)) {\n            $tokenData[$t] = @{ freq = 0; cfi_denom = 0; cfi_numer = 0 }\n            $tokenDocs[$t] = 0\n        }\n        $tokenData[$t].freq++\n        $docTokens[$t] = $true  # track unique doc presence\n    }\n    \n    # Count docs per token (for IDF-like signal)\n    foreach ($t in $docTokens.Keys) {\n        $tokenDocs[$t]++\n    }\n}\n\n# Calculate CFI for each token\n$totalDocs = $pulseFiles.Count\n$allTokens = @($tokenData.Keys) | Sort-Object { $tokenData[$_].freq } -Descending\n\nWrite-Host \"Total unique tokens: $($allTokens.Count)\"\n\n# CFI calculation: token appears in what fraction of all docs?\nforeach ($tok in $allTokens) {\n    $tokenData[$tok].cfi = [Math]::Round($tokenDocs[$tok] / $totalDocs, 4)\n}\n\n# Calculate hybrid score: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\n$scoredTokens = @()\nforeach ($tok in $allTokens) {\n    $freq = $tokenData[$tok].freq\n    $cfi = $tokenData[$tok].cfi\n    $freqFactor = [Math]::Min(1, $freq / 120)\n    $score = [Math]::Round($cfi * $freqFactor, 4)\n    \n    $scoredTokens += [PSCustomObject]@{\n        Token = $tok\n        Freq = $freq\n        CFI = $cfi\n        FreqFactor = $freqFactor\n        HybridScore = $score\n        Docs = $tokenDocs[$tok]\n    }\n}\n\n# Sort by hybrid score descending\n$scoredTokens = $scoredTokens\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774380048747}}
{"type":"message","id":"b45a1c0a","parentId":"c1265b8b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:20:55.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me summarize the pulse results.","thinkingSignature":"5c0a08eff50494384a2fa1b7a487d8a50895717df833e33d2de435da2b0253ac"},{"type":"text","text":"**Sandbox Pulse Summary — 2026-03-24 15:20 UTC**\n\n**What happened:**\n1. Previous mutation (hybrid scoring script, `pulse_2026-03-24 151918.mutation`) was **rejected** — no action taken\n2. A new mutation was proposed: a PowerShell script implementing the **CFI×Freq hybrid scoring experiment** (Strategy C)\n3. Script creates `CFI_FREQ_HYBRID_RESULTS.md` comparing hybrid score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq/120) against binary thresholds\n4. 6 files changed (+296/-86 lines) — session log and mutation file created\n\n**Current state:**\n- Previous binary experiment (CFI ≥ 0.7, freq < 60) was **too aggressive** — 92.9% recall loss\n- Key insight: \"Phase 1\" tokens (freq=136, CFI=0.96) are true research trajectory crushed by freq < 60 cap\n- **Pending action:** Run the new hybrid scoring experiment to test if score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq/120) handles both constant-format (freq≈160, CFI=1) and research trajectory better than binary filters"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5329,"output":285,"cacheRead":12245,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17859,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774380048750}}
